<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٢ - <span class="c1">"الإكمال"</span> لابن ماكولا <span class="c2">(٤/ ٥١)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٣ - <span class="c1">"الأنساب"</span> للسمعاني <span class="c2">(٧/ ١٧٦)</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٤ - <span class="c1">"تبصير المنتبه"</span> للحافظ ابن حجر <span class="c2">(٢/ ٧٥٤)</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>٥ - <span class="c1">"تذكرة الحفّاظ"</span> للذهبي <span class="c2">(٣/ ٩٣٩ - ٩٤٠)</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>٦ - <span class="c1">"توضيح المشتبه"</span> لابن ناصر الدّين الدّمشقي <span class="c2">(٥/ ١٩٤)</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>٧ - <span class="c1">"سير أعلام النبلاء"</span> للذهبي <span class="c2">(١٦/ ٢٥٥ - ٢٥٧)</span>.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>٨ - <span class="c1">"شذرات الذّهب"</span> لابن العماد الحنبلي <span class="c2">(٣/ ٤٧)</span>.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>٩ - <span class="c1">"طبقات الشافعيّة الكبرى"</span> للسُّبكي <span class="c2">(٢/ ٩٦)</span>.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>١٠ - <span class="c1">"العبر في خبر من غبر"</span> للذهبي <span class="c2">(٢/ ١١٩ - ١٢٠)</span>.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
